    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Assume you want to create a travel website. It has a feature of book ticket. For this you need to create frontend (UI page). But you don&amp;rsquo;t want to create ticket for any unauthorized person and you don&amp;rsquo;t want to implement the authentication and authorization on your website.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
